              "free_text": [
                " Recoil protons momentum analyzed in medium",
                " resolution spectrometer.",
                "Protons at large angles blocked by shielding or are",
                " bent by small dipole magnet placed between target and",
                " recoil scintillator. Thin plastic scintillator placed",
                " just before recoil scintillator to veto protons or",
                " neutral atomic hydrogen.",
                "Scattered neutrons detected using CH2 liquid",
                " scintillator; scintillator material BC513 (BICRON).",
                "Two front end wire chambers placed after recoil",
                " scintillator to track protons, followed by quadrupole",
                " magnet.",
                "Beam polarization monitored using in-beam polarimeter",
                " consisting of a thin CH2 target and plastic",
                " scintillators to detect p-p elastic scattering."
              ]
            }
